Be cautious about mixing magical and mundane extracts/filtered items in complex combinations, as this can often reduce value. Examples of successful combinations include Mandrake Root Extract + filtered morning dew/honey nectar, or dragon scale extract + filtered tree sap, or bat wing extract + filtered basilisk venom.
